node.text: Ants are nature's engineers 🐜💪

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'UNILAD TECH Sponge fossils suggest animals already existed 890 million years'.

node.text: A fossil discovered in northwestern Canada could rewrite the early history of animal life, but some palaeontologists are not convinced it’s even real.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on August 02, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text that says 'UNILAD TECH A giant Tesla battery pack burst into flames during testing, and it took 150 firefighters 4 days to put out'.

node.text: The CFA and Fire Rescue Victoria responded to the incident, which started about 10.30am on Friday morning. They found a 13-tonne lithium battery inside a shipping container was fully involved and crews wearing breathing apparatus worked to contain the fire and stop it spreading to nearby batteries. 🔥👀

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by UNILAD Tech on August 02, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'News Nearly 14,000 scientists warn that Earth's 'vital signs' rerapidly worsening'.

node.text: Researchers wrote in BioScience, "We are nearing or have already crossed tipping points associated with critical parts of the Earth system, including the West Antarctic and Greenland ice sheets, warm-water coral reefs, and the Amazon rainforest," 🌍😬
